What you need to know:

For starters, Kremlev, who is the first AIBA president to visit Africa, will help Boxing Federation of Kenya (BFK) put up a boxing arena that will be furnished with a modern boxing gymnasium at the Moi International Sports Centre, KasaraniAt the same time the Aiba president disclosed that Kenya will be the venue for the first Africa international tournament that will be used to unite African boxersOkudo commended Kremlev and BFK leadership for the initiative that will explore ways of developing boxing in Kenya and the continent in such a way that the game can be a way of life for those participating in that ecosystem